    dc:description "FIGURE 7 A – I. Notophthiracarus otwayensis Niedbała sp. nov. (holotype). A, prodorsum, dorsal view; B, prodorsum, lateral view; C, opisthosoma, lateral view; D, seta c 1; E, mentum of subcapitulum; F, left genitoaggenital plate; G, right anoadanal plates; H, trochanter and femur of leg I; I, seta d of femur I. Scale bars 100 µm (A – C, F, G), 50 µm (D, E, H), 10 µm (I)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1042275/files/figure.png" ;
